# Home Inventory — local secrets (DO NOT COMMIT)

Copy this file to `secrets.local.md` and fill in real values.
`secrets.local.md` is gitignored. Never rename this example to hold real URLs in git.

## Web App URL (Deploy → Manage deployments)
GAS_WEB_APP_URL=https://script.google.com/macros/s/your-deployment-id/exec

## Drive folder id (from folder URL …/folders/FOLDER_ID)
DRIVE_FOLDER_ID=your-folder-id

## Spreadsheet link (optional private bookmark; not required by the app)
SHEET_URL=https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/your-sheet-id/edit
